lead_paragraph: Stricker holed out from the 10th fairway for eagle on his way to a five-under-par 66 that gave him a share of the lead with Will MacKenzie in the Valspar Championship in Palm Harbor, Fla.

headline.main: Steve Stricker Is Tied for Lead in Valspar Championship
